{"tid":1991391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE考新聞自由 但事實係我哋都無新聞自由","createTime":"2020-04-27T11:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T12:20:49.000Z","uid":101994,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"549e9f1cd6e2e386821bbfa62314caf13ce2d44b","tid":1991391,"uid":101994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:35:06.000Z","msg":"今日睇咗依單報導<br />\n<br />\n【瀕臨失聲的香港（二）：衝擊第四權】<br />\n【暴政打壓血濺第四權 傳媒監察處風口浪尖】<br />\n<br />\n由去年反修例運動至今，記者採訪時被警方稱為「黑記」、遭受暴力對待、侵犯私隱、阻礙採訪、甚至被捕，但有關投訴至今未有一宗成立，而記者採訪受威脅的風險愈來愈高。記者以生命捍衛真相，換來的是否只能夠啞忍暴力？我們的第四權和新聞自由，是否已經走上末路呢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/videos/2503567843240273?vh=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcantonese.rfa%2Fvideos%2F2503567843240273%3Fvh%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4X6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=2fcf5416\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/videos/2503567843240273?vh=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n好感慨<br />\n昇哥講得啱，新聞自由係要我哋去爭取<br />\n記者都係手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直遭受黑警暴力都無得出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一國兩制真心依加渣都無呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e982cd047e678754a78fd3de1bb38eef2472517","tid":1991391,"uid":101994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:40:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a488dff2ee556ca18a54df05b4c26245eb67f30","tid":1991391,"uid":101994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"549e9f1cd6e2e386821bbfa62314caf13ce2d44b","tid":1991391,"uid":101994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:35:06.000Z","msg":"今日睇咗依單報導<br />\n<br />\n【瀕臨失聲的香港（二）：衝擊第四權】<br />\n【暴政打壓血濺第四權 傳媒監察處風口浪尖】<br />\n<br />\